cannabis seemed like

36:44.402 --> 36:46.137 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a good choice for me.

36:46.171 --> 36:51.609 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Arbelaez believes
this classic
old bank is brick-and-mortar
proof pot is

36:51.643 --> 36:56.681 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
