37:43.995 --> 37:50.602 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
award. Raphael Mechoulam is an
Israeli chemist
who became interested in
cannabis when he

37:50.635 --> 37:52.504 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
