national history.

39:23.494 --> 39:29.067 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: In the U.S.,
marijuana still
remains classified as a Schedule
1 controlled

39:29.100 --> 39:35.440 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
substance, the same category as
heroin, cocaine
and LSD, with tight restrictions
for researchers

39:35.473 --> 39:38.543 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and no accepted use for medical
treatment.

39:38.576 --> 39:44.449 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
