homemade doses
of CBD, at times making the
formula in her

42:14.132 --> 42:15.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
garage.

42:15.433 --> 42:18.202 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
His seizures diminished by 40
percent.

42:18.236 --> 42:24.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CATHERINE JACOBSON: But it's
excruciating
to think about what we went
through to get

42:24.308 --> 42:29.914 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
here, right, and what might have
happened
if we have been able to do this
five years

42:29.947 --> 42:31.716 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ago or six years ago.

42:31.749 --> 42:35.620 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I know for a fact he would be a
different
kid today if he hadn't suffered
all that brain

42:35.653 --> 42:37.455 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
damage.

42:37.488 --> 42:41.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Her experience
with her son
and CBD prompted her to redirect
her scientific

42:41.793 --> 42:50.234 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
career. She now heads clinical
research for
Tilray, a Canadian medical
marijuana company

42:50.268 --> 42:53.271 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
trying to turn cannabis into
conventional
medicine.

